@startuml
title game-lib stage runtime class diagram

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype ortho
skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0
hide empty members
hide circle

package "Author-facing stage layer" {
  class Stage <<wrapper>>
  class StageConfig <<config>>
  class CameraWrapper <<camera api>>
}

package "Live stage runtime" {
  class ZylemStage <<runtime>>
  class StageEntityDelegate <<delegate>>
  class StageCameraDelegate <<delegate>>
  class StageLoadingDelegate <<delegate>>
  class StageEntityModelDelegate <<delegate>>
  class StageDebugDelegate <<delegate>>
}

package "Scene / physics / rendering collaborators" {
  class ZylemScene
  class ZylemWorld
  class CameraManager
  class RendererManager
  class InstanceManager
}

package "Entities / behaviors" {
  abstract class BaseNode
  class GameEntity
  interface BehaviorSystem
}

package "Events" {
  class GameEventBus <<event bus>>
}

BaseNode <|-- GameEntity

Stage --> StageConfig : parses options into
Stage --> CameraWrapper : add / remove / activate
Stage *-- ZylemStage : creates at load time

ZylemStage *-- StageEntityDelegate
ZylemStage *-- StageCameraDelegate
ZylemStage *-- StageLoadingDelegate
ZylemStage *-- StageEntityModelDelegate
ZylemStage *-- StageDebugDelegate

ZylemStage *-- ZylemScene
ZylemStage *-- ZylemWorld
ZylemStage *-- InstanceManager
ZylemStage o-- CameraManager

StageCameraDelegate --> CameraManager : configures effective camera set
CameraWrapper --> CameraManager : becomes managed camera
CameraManager --> RendererManager : renders through

StageEntityDelegate --> BaseNode : spawns / tracks
StageEntityDelegate --> GameEntity : attaches physics + models
StageEntityDelegate --> BehaviorSystem : auto-registers per behavior key

StageEntityModelDelegate --> StageEntityDelegate : model-ready callbacks
StageLoadingDelegate --> GameEventBus : forwards loading events
StageDebugDelegate --> ZylemScene : helpers / overlays / picking
StageDebugDelegate --> CameraManager : uses active camera
ZylemWorld --> GameEntity : body sync + collisions
InstanceManager --> GameEntity : batches instanced entities
InstanceManager --> ZylemScene : writes instanced meshes

note right of Stage
Author-facing wrapper.

Collects:
- entities
- cameras
- lifecycle callbacks
- input overrides

The wrapper exists before the live
runtime is created.
end note

note right of ZylemStage
Live stage coordinator.

Owns:
- scene
- physics world
- entity/camera/loading/debug delegates
- runtime update + teardown flow
end note

note bottom of StageEntityDelegate
Central entity runtime manager.

Responsibilities:
- queue / spawn / remove nodes
- maintain UUID/EID mappings
- attach physics bodies and colliders
- register instancing
- link behaviors to stage systems
end note

note bottom of StageCameraDelegate
Resolves the effective camera setup:
- explicit cameras
- multi-camera layouts
- fallback default camera
end note

note right of RendererManager
Shared renderer infrastructure.
A stage reaches it indirectly through
CameraManager rather than owning it directly.
end note

legend left
|= Layer |= Role |
| Stage | author-facing configuration wrapper |
| ZylemStage | live runtime orchestrator |
| Delegates | focused stage subsystems |
| Scene / World / Camera | rendering + physics collaborators |
| BaseNode / GameEntity | runtime content managed by the stage |
endlegend

@enduml
